---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Roadmap | Superior"
  description="Release ladder for Superior: practice money now, replay depth next, live still locked."
>
  <section class="machine-page">
    <header class="machine-page__header">
      <div class="machine-page__title">
        <span class="machine-page__label">Roadmap</span>
        <strong>Practice world / release ladder</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="machine-page__status">LOCAL / $100 START / LIVE LOCKED</div>
    </header>

    <div class="machine-page__body machine-page__body--single">
      <div class="machine-page__column">
        <div class="machine-page__block">
          <span>Current shape</span>
          <strong>Start with $100. Replay. Compare presets. Keep live off.</strong>
          <p>Ship the practice loop first. Add more depth only after the fake-money run feels clean and repeatable.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="machine-page__rail">
          <article class="machine-page__strip">
            <span class="machine-page__strip-label">Now</span>
            <div class="machine-page__strip-body">
              <strong>Tape packs</strong>
              <p>More tutorial and replay chapters, bankroll carry, and preset comparisons that teach timing through repetition.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="machine-page__strip">
            <span class="machine-page__strip-label">Next</span>
            <div class="machine-page__strip-body">
              <strong>Daily run</strong>
              <p>One deterministic challenge per day, one saved result, same tape for everyone, no extra menu sprawl.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="machine-page__strip">
            <span class="machine-page__strip-label">Later</span>
            <div class="machine-page__strip-body">
              <strong>Deeper practice</strong>
              <p>Harder tapes, longer runs, and more replay depth once the core loop proves it can hold regular use.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="machine-page__strip">
            <span class="machine-page__strip-label">Not now</span>
            <div class="machine-page__strip-body">
              <strong>No hosted live bot</strong>
              <p>No cloud runtime, no always-on money mode, and no credentials in the first-run path.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <nav class="machine-page__controls" aria-label="Roadmap controls">
      <a class="machine-page__control machine-page__control--primary" href="/download/">
        <span>Download</span>
      </a>
      <a class="machine-page__control machine-page__control--secondary" href="/docs/">
        <span>Docs</span>
      </a>
      <a class="machine-page__control machine-page__control--commit" href="/lab/">
        <span>Variants</span>
      </a>
      <a class="machine-page__control machine-page__control--reset" href="https://github.com/Zwin-ux/arbitrage" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
        <span>GitHub</span>
      </a>
    </nav>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
